'''Phrikite''' was the source ore for the metal [[Phrik/Legends|phrik]]. Its primary source was [[Gromas 16]].

==Behind the scenes==
According to a mission in the video-game ''[[Star Wars: DroidWorks]]'' from [[Lucas Learning]], [[Phrik/Legends|phrik]] deposits are also found on [[Tatooine/Legends|Tatooine]]. The player visits a phrik mine and extracts some of the metal to keep their facility running.

